- Bajingan kecil!

225
00:24:11,615 --> 00:24:12,775
Ayo, bajingan kecil!

226
00:24:12,935 --> 00:24:15,135
Mau lari ke mana kau?

227
00:24:26,255 --> 00:24:27,615
Jase?

228
00:24:32,455 --> 00:24:34,175
Marcus!

229
00:25:01,215 --> 00:25:02,775
Jason?

230
00:25:03,215 --> 00:25:04,215
Jason?

231
00:25:04,415 --> 00:25:06,815
Aku mohon, Jason.

232
00:25:06,975 --> 00:25:09,975
Jason, ayolah.
Aku membutuhkanmu.

233
00:25:10,135 --> 00:25:11,655
Aku mohon.

234
00:25:11,855 --> 00:25:13,535
Ayolah.

235
00:25:13,895 --> 00:25:15,055
Jason!

236
00:25:15,255 --> 00:25:18,855
Jason, ayolah.
Kumohon, Jase.

237
00:25:19,015 --> 00:25:20,695
Jase.

238
00:25:56,735 --> 00:25:59,255
Aku merasa bersalah. Mestinya aku
tetap tinggal untuk meliput beritanya.

239
00:25:59,775 --> 00:26:01,615
Setelah apa yang menimpamu?

240
00:26:02,255 --> 00:26:04,455
Mereka mengirim satu kru
dari kantor di Hong Kong.

241
00:26:05,975 --> 00:26:07,615
Aku tak pernah lakukan itu...

242
00:26:07,815 --> 00:26:09,295
...menghindar dari berita
