Ya.

840
01:16:56,215 --> 01:16:57,935
Selain tahu atau merasakan
segala sesuatu?

841
01:16:58,095 --> 01:16:59,295
Tepat sekali.

842
01:16:59,495 --> 01:17:01,655
- Kau mau teh?
